  "items": [
    {
      "key": "frontendmenu_update9popup_desc",
      "source": "Update 8 is here, and it's ready for the season with the returning Festive Scenery pack, and new Adverse Weather! Keep your guests sheltered from frightening Thunderstorms, and put down a heater or two to stop your pools freezing over once the Snow starts falling! Check the Planet Coaster website for full Update Notes.\n\nThe Toybox Pack is now available, and it's bringing two new coasters: the exhilarating Vector New-Gen Inverting Suspended, and the fantastic F&N Thriller Industries Kid Coaster! Also included are three playful new flat rides: the Airdrop, Highroll and the totally tubular WaveSim! Crank the fun up to the max with heroic new entertainer Max Stormcloud, and get creative with all the arts, crafts, and classic toys bursting out of the Toybox Scenery pack. Some self-assembly required. The Toybox pack, available now! Wippi yalapler!",
      "context": "",
      "max_length": null
    },
